{"tid":2197982,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"廣告設計師被控襲警及管有噴漆 鄭紀航裁定罪名成立 判監5個半月 即時駁回被告保釋等候上訴申請","createTime":"2020-09-11T04:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T15:25:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"46082196bbe04f170065f10391d9808fcb52bca5","tid":2197982,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:36:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9297\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F9297&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=f8cabbb0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/9297</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第五庭<br />\n#鄭紀航裁判官<br />\n#裁決<br />\n#1102中環<br />\n<br />\n👤張(22)<br />\n<br />\n控罪：(1) 襲警 <br />\n           (2) 管有物品意圖損壞財產<br />\n<br />\n案情：被控於2019年11月2日，在中環砵典乍街18號外，襲擊執行警務的警員，即高級督察韋鑑洸；另被控於同日同地保管或控制兩支噴漆。<br />\n<br />\n被告2項罪名成立‼️<br />\n<br />\n判刑：‼️2項控罪刑期部份分期執行，合共5個月15天即時監禁‼️<br />\n<br />\n詳情後補....."},{"pid":"04917be5d237d0c2fced1e149abc7efb6ba5f518","tid":2197982,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d4f4c8def7da540db23a49f6ed95da189575ed","tid":2197982,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04917be5d237d0c2fced1e149abc7efb6ba5f518","tid":2197982,"uid":274532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05a58f297ecfb7f8d2959def702f64d2f7c5cb9","tid":2197982,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c